---
export const prerender = true;
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Editorial Policy | Home Nesto"
  description="Understand how Home Nesto creates, reviews, and updates content to maintain quality and transparency."
>
  <section class="py-14 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Editorial Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-8">Last updated: May 18, 2026</p>
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl border border-gray-100 p-6 md:p-8 space-y-6 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
        <p>
          Our goal is to publish helpful, accurate, and easy-to-understand real estate content. This policy explains how we create and
          maintain content on Home Nesto.
        </p>
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Content Standards</h2>
          <p>
            We prioritize clarity, relevance, and factual accuracy. We avoid sensational claims and clearly separate informational
            content from promotional material.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Sources</h2>
          <p>
            Sources may include publicly available information, developer-provided materials, and on-ground inputs. Where details are
            uncertain or subject to change, we aim to state that clearly.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Corrections</h2>
          <p>
            If you notice an error, please contact{' '}
            <a class="text-primary-700 hover:text-primary-800" href="mailto:editorial@homenesto.com">editorial@homenesto.com</a>.
            We review and update content when warranted.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

